Create the IoT Rule (The Bridge)
This is the "Logic" that connects your ESP32 to your Database.

Go to AWS IoT Core > Message Routing > Rules.

Click Create Rule.

Rule name: RouteToDynamoDB.

SQL Statement:

SQL
SELECT * FROM 'attendance/scan'
Attach an Action:

Choose DynamoDBv2 (Put a message into a DynamoDB table).

Select your table: StudentAttendance.

IAM Role: Click "Create new role," name it IoTToDynamoRole. This gives AWS IoT permission to write into your database.

Click Create.
